{"id": 1594, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在生活中见过哪些好笑的小型攀比行为？", "description": "无处不 battle，输什么也不能输了尊严。", "record_count": 5648, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201703301154100erpuaBINgHKlEA2.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-30T03:00:01Z", "options": [{"id": 198144, "content": "严肃场合透露自己做了什么她自己认为很了不起的“大事儿”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011736}, {"id": 185600, "content": "舍友偷瞄你换睡衣～然后默默看看自己的身材", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905971}, {"id": 192769, "content": "考试之前不复习，也要吵得别人都不能复习(๑•ั็ω•็ั๑)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1005686}, {"id": 185603, "content": "餓了嗎和美團的騎手在紅燈熄滅的那一刻上演速度與激情。是兩家外賣無法收斂的歡呼！", "image": "img/option/option/20170330144454e5ZHuj2lXJLOsiTP.jpg", "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 73247}, {"id": 185604, "content": "室友:我是你爸爸，我:傻儿子，室友:狗儿子。这样的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652241}, {"id": 186116, "content": "比谁穷", "image": "img/option/option/20170401095109xmTSjp9AsQdPrHac.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946202}, {"id": 191237, "content": "室友上课看你做笔记就努力做笔记，要不然就不经意的看你写了什么做了什么。你上课不听耍手机她也开始耍手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984353}, {"id": 185094, "content": "夜跑的时候“xiu”地跑到前面去，结果还不是得在前面红绿灯原地踏步哼", "image": null, "praise_count": 120, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 185606, "content": "我惨...\r\n\r\n我更惨~", "image": null, "praise_count": 191, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987379}, {"id": 192262, "content": "玩游戏比谁看的联赛多更有意识…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986779}, {"id": 185095, "content": "蚂蚁森林里比谁树大，看长得快就天天来偷能量，绝不浇水", "image": null, "praise_count": 653, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 185607, "content": "办公室的人老拿胸说事儿，其实每个人都长了，你说呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987350}, {"id": 188679, "content": "你男朋友比我男朋友家里有钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956251}, {"id": 185608, "content": "b站视频开头的弹幕，各种第一……", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 192776, "content": "明明是想诉个苦，\n结果“我才惨好不好”\n然后莫名其妙开始讲自己的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998566}, {"id": 185609, "content": "比谁的数学作业做得快。【微笑】", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834849}, {"id": 187145, "content": "我去过哪里旅游我去过哪里。。，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889364}, {"id": 185611, "content": "大学中文系。老师上课讲了什么作品是和高中内容有关的，非和舍友说高中怎样怎样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 959568}, {"id": 185612, "content": "室友们都不下去买饭比谁更懒~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979573}, {"id": 185868, "content": "跟老婆比今天谁更丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988290}, {"id": 190733, "content": "谈论某件事时，那个人总能说你不是，然后说他认识的人有这样的经历，然后巴拉巴拉一堆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001856}, {"id": 185614, "content": "跟四川人爱吃辣?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987403}, {"id": 186638, "content": "看谁用的手机好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712085}, {"id": 186894, "content": "放假，看谁来加班，加班，看谁走的晚", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477475}, {"id": 185103, "content": "跑步机上拼死也要等旁边的人先停", "image": null, "praise_count": 217, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 185616, "content": "我舍友居然在比谁洗澡快，不知道哪里来的优越感~", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 102092}, {"id": 206609, "content": "说牛逼亲戚的那位，太同意了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122651}, {"id": 185105, "content": "汗蒸比谁待得久", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 187153, "content": "学校里攀比电子表\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667210}, {"id": 212498, "content": "一双安踏的鞋，说了一年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053790}, {"id": 185618, "content": "微博上看到的，我在压腿别人就在我旁边劈叉，健身房充满了battle", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887037}, {"id": 185107, "content": "按脚比谁能忍住不叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 185619, "content": "每次打斗和男朋友比较 你打我比我打你多了一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987404}, {"id": 185620, "content": "胸", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966728}, {"id": 189972, "content": "我长得比你黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999138}, {"id": 185621, "content": "健身房不battle，和公园有什么区别", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977460}, {"id": 186133, "content": "我好穷～我更穷～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989174}, {"id": 185622, "content": "小众独立跟大众流行？", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786145}, {"id": 185878, "content": "分手之后比谁先找到下一任。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987241}, {"id": 189206, "content": "买了衣服，会强调原价是多少", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996879}, {"id": 185624, "content": "室友早上没课也要定闹钟抢我的绿色能量", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987427}, {"id": 185625, "content": "泡澡总是比别人后出来一些，间隔不超过一分钟，干！烫死老子了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530513}, {"id": 187929, "content": "和室友做平板支撑，两人比谁先撑到目标，虽然目标只有一分钟?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993381}, {"id": 187162, "content": "什么什么名著我小学看过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991871}, {"id": 185627, "content": "健身房的攀比", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987438}, {"id": 188699, "content": "坐公交回家还是打车回家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995185}, {"id": 194075, "content": "买个游戏机还有鄙视链。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962364}, {"id": 185629, "content": "微博粉丝数", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967240}, {"id": 188445, "content": "我的男朋友多么多么优秀……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994376}, {"id": 185630, "content": "总是把自己身边的人说的特别厉害?，\n我就不明白了，别人是别人，你是你啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986363}]}